  "texts": [
    "Curiosity was rated the highest of these skills, indicating that students found ChatGPT especially effective in stimulating their interest and engagement with academic material.",
    "In contrast, management skills received the lowest rating, suggesting that noticeable improvements in some areas are not universally experienced.",
    "Within the context of professional skills enhancement, a recent study demonstrated the potential of ChatGPT in producing vignettes based on specific diseases, which can serve as an important educational source [4].",
    "In nursing education, ChatGPT offers opportunities for personalized learning, simulation scenarios, and immediate feedback [24], while medical students use ChatGPT to simplify complex concepts, create mnemonics, and enhance patient communication skills [15].",
    "The AI tool has also demonstrated proficiency in clinical reasoning, famously achieving near-passing scores for medical licensing exams [15]."
